Level

Class Level

  • java.lang.Object
    • Level.Level
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    RandomLevel, SpawnLevel

    public abstract class Level
extends java.lang.Object
    Class for game levels; int[] tiles means that at index 0 can be tile grass, at 1 can be tile stone etc.
